 you see. But I - when I got like say twelve years old I got a job then see, I was - I - I was lucky because I got some food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7745245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4540718 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 Yes. She was an angel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7745245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 Did she show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4540718 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 Yes.
