ht or something and my mother said something about that I - that she - she went across the school fetch me back - out, because I hadn't washed, I didn't wash when I come back. I'd washed in the morning, cleaned me boots. But I never washed when I come hom
e, I - I would be late - before I left school. She went and fetched me at school. I can remember her - Mr }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1399755\charrsid9580092 Hawkins}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 
