\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1399755\charrsid9580092 My father - beat it into you, you see, but my mother - no.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7745245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 She taught you by example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4540718 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 Yes. Try and help other - she would all - help - help - help other people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7745245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 What did they think of swearing?
