No. No. No, no, he wouldn't - he was like my - that brother I tell you about. He wouldn't be disciplined - he would - in the Army, yes, he was a soldier. I me
an he wouldn't be able to do that. But you talking about what they used to do then was get like - political - talk like about sort of - this - local government and all, well what did they used to do was take them all in the public house, the Albion or any
 
public house you like and treat 'em to beer and all that did they - these - 'course they're not allowed to do it now. But it used to be done in them days. I don't know so much about the general elections. But the old - the local elections, like my father'
