 name was William and they'd - Bill, come on, what're you going to have with me Bill? Well you're a jolly good fellow and chat around and of course - my father drinking, he'd - if he weren't on his side he'd say yes, you're getting my vote, while he's get
ting this.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7745245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 As long he was getting the beer?
