\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7745245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 They were more exclusive?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4540718 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 That's what it is, yes. Well I mean a working man couldn't afford to belong to one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7745245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 Do you remember him working for one of the parties at an election?
