Oh he - he wouldn't go out not - for the party but I've been talking round, yes. Not - not for - say to the - candidate I'll be a - I'm working for you, never went to all that, no, but he let everybody know what he t
hought. Oh yes. He liked to be heard. Like me, a big chatterer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7745245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 Did your parents take part in any political activities other than at election times?
