\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4540718 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5376311\charrsid9580092 Well we'd have a walk round and all that, have 
